00:04:01.316 --> 00:04:05.028
- 1.1, 1.1, I could
put that in parentheses

00:04:05.028 --> 00:04:07.089
just to make it clear, and then all

00:04:07.089 --> 00:04:08.850
of that is going to be over,

00:04:08.850 --> 00:04:12.800
well -3.1 + 3 is going to be,

