the positive direction,

00:04:54.942 --> 00:04:57.871
and that's what this
notation over there means,

00:04:57.871 --> 00:04:59.433
this superscript on the right hand

00:04:59.433 --> 00:05:01.154
side, the positive direction,

00:05:01.154 --> 00:05:04.400
so we're going to approach x
from the positive direction,

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:06.554
and I'm going to pay
attention in particular

00:05:06.554 --> 00:05:10.138
to the interval between -2 and -3,

00:05:10.138 --> 00:05:11.642
because then we know
we don't have any weird

00:05:11.642 --> 00:05:13.579
